  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">With the high rate of school dropout and missing out of school activities due to inaccessible period products, the Red Dots provides comfortable and clean reusable pads and pant liners for menstruators to keep them in school.   The period kit also has an illustrative menstrual education and a customizable period calendar to aid period tracking. Pads last between three to five years.</narrative>
